      <title>欧洲央行连续第三次降息以提振疲软的经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ecb-interest-rates-third-straight-cut-will-help-support-eurozone-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行连续第三次下调利率，暗示由于通胀率接近 2% 且经济陷入困境，明年将进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ecb-interest-rates-third-straight-cut-will-help-support-eurozone-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 13:22:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
